Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}『WOLF字幕組』      (www.wolfsub.com)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾出本山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日復一日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羊腸小路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安達之原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}節選自謠曲:『黑塚』舞者表演的為日本傳統舞台藝術『能』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人 不是鐮倉的兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 不過想殺源義經的並非只有您哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:05:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知還有多少人想要取您的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源氏從平家手中奪取天下之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最為危險的就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弁慶 你若取下我的人頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少還能保住性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輩已經活得夠久 戰得夠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 到此結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎能這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 弁慶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎少爺 那裏有火光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火光？ 是追兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那火光沒有移動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應是人家的燈光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道還有人住在這深山裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除我們之外還有其他遠離俗世之人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天色已晚 水也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是人家 就去借宿一晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎之名暫由我弁慶代為使用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問有人在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何貴幹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我是自紀州熊野而來 周遊各國的僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名為九郎坊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路經此山時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適逢天色已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土間或屋檐都行 能否讓我們在此借宿一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}土間：日本以前民居中露出泥地的房間 一般為進屋後脫鞋的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決不會給您添麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的隨同…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高的燒 不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是你的弟子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但您的身上有難以掩飾的高貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿那位僧侶才是您的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以讓你們住下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一個要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這屋子最裏面有個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的閨房
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裏面久未整理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何請不要往裏看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 小事一樁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能答應這個要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都可以住在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好一點了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還沒有太大起色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算下山買些藥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這期間 那位大人就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燒已經退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是您在照顧我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說好借宿一晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等同伴回來我們馬上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要您願意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論多久都可以住在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論多久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏和我至今所在的世界完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它存在於時間和空間之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 就是這些樹木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經活了上千年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天您會離開這兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概是瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論我們再怎麼彼此相愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命運決定了我和您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不能在一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弁慶回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是弁慶的話應該會先來這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是裏間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何請不要往裏看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您覺得我很骯髒是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道總會有這樣一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我心中一直無意識地 盼望著您能看到這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天看到的一切我不會告訴別人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我贏了 義經
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說那個女人不會死？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其女命逾百年而不老 乃不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾族從平安京時代起就一直追殺著她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老丈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你準備抓她來如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解開……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體不同常人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本不想讓您知道這骯髒之軀的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經活不長了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就會死在這荒山裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我留下 自己逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您願與我同行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間的盡頭

